sourcesContent: import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'; import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'; function ForeCastText(props) { let { current: { feelslike_c, uv, wind_kph, humidity } } = props.weather; return ( Real Feel {feelslike_c}°C Wind {wind_kph} Km/h {/* Humidity {humidity} % UV Index {uv} */} ) } export default ForeCastText;
